{"TopicId":132564,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"WW2 BAD-T 2 - BDA AI Dogfight Tournament [SEMIFINALS]","CreatedByName":"tetryds","CreatedById":50204,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T17:46:10Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Pds314","CreatedById":70014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T18:08:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429325\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456423586\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022115126\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MightyDarkStar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, MightyDarkStar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWarspite F. 20 Fighter\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDimensions: (Length) - 10.2 metres, (Wingspan) - 22.4 metres, (Weight) - 4.61 tons\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nParts: 29, Points: 86\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWeaponry: 1x\u00A0 \u003Cb style=\u0022color:rgb(37,37,37);font-family:sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003EVolkov-Yartsev VYa-23\u00A0\u003C/b\u003E23mm autocannon in the propeller hub, 2x \u003Cstrong\u003EMauser MG 131/13\u003C/strong\u003E 13mm machineguns under the wing roots\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPowerplant: \u003Cstrong\u003ERoaken B37-D \u0022Buzzer\u0022\u003C/strong\u003E Radial Engine\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoly cow! 22.4m in span! and I thought some of my designs were ridiculously wide at 17 meters..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MightyDarkStar","CreatedById":115126,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T18:15:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429331\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456423737\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pds314\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Pds314 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoly cow! 22.4m in span! and I thought some of my designs were ridiculously wide at 17 meters..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt might be big, but it\u0027s capable of 468 mph (772 kp/h) and is comparable to the Spitfire in agility. Not to mention that for its size it is very light for a KSP ship.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Doke","CreatedById":149975,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T18:21:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222428907\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456395949\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KamikazeF0X\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, KamikazeF0X said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn fact, 20 units of fuel lasts for something like 20 minutes, I am someone who likes to have a lots of things\u003Cbr\u003E\nLots of ammo, lots of guns, lots of fuel and -the most important- a lots of snaks ! ^^\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFair enough. FAR\u0027s readout gives my plane 1-2 hours at full power with 20 units, but it might of course be wrong. Fuel is a relatively small weight on these planes, anyway (compared to afterburning jets).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429070\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456409953\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo after some testing and aero design changes I have decided that I will enter my DF-43 Bad Company into this competition\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can find a teaser video of her in action\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/ZtaQKEgd2DE\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E HERE \u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E... The game clip was taken during tuning\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are still a few gremlins to wash out but she performs admirably\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really like this design. Reminds me of something from Crimson Skies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429177\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456416328\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274479\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pyrosheep\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, pyrosheep said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EReveal hidden contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/nBWZI3cze3k?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is a dummy battle with my updated design.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNifty. What\u0027s that thing behind the pilot?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TangerineSedge","CreatedById":150386,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T19:25:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222428317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456354419\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250204\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tetryds\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, tetryds said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2x 30mm, that is a nice choice, does it crunch the dummy on a single pass?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNormally, yes. And I\u0027ll post some pics soon\u00A0of my alternative that I decided against due to it being...problematic. I think \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149975-doke/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149975\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149975-doke/\u0022\u003E@Doke\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0should recognize it at least.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pyrosheep","CreatedById":74479,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T19:27:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429350\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456424488\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Doke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, Doke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNifty. What\u0027s that thing behind the pilot?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe white thing is the fuel tank, it may not seem particularly safe there, but it isn\u0027t unusual to have the pilot practically sitting on\u00A0the fuel IRL\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Bf-109-0307-05-0-1_zpsfee67522.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i843.photobucket.com/albums/zz354/micksbike/Bf-109-0307-05-0-1_zpsfee67522.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KamikazeF0X","CreatedById":104217,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T19:29:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429454\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456428460\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274479\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pyrosheep\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, pyrosheep said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe white thing is the fuel tank, it may not seem particularly safe there, but it isn\u0027t unusual to have the pilot practically sitting on\u00A0the fuel IRL\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could put fuel in the wings too\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pyrosheep","CreatedById":74479,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T19:36:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456428544\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KamikazeF0X\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, KamikazeF0X said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could put fuel in the wings too\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe centre of mass would move back as it drains, changing the aircraft\u0027s stability through the battle;\u00A0this could lead to spins.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would also move the mass outwards, i think this would make\u00A0the craft roll less well\u00A0(though not by too much).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KamikazeF0X","CreatedById":104217,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T19:40:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429472\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456428964\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274479\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pyrosheep\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, pyrosheep said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe centre of mass would move back as it drains, changing the aircraft\u0027s stability through the battle;\u00A0this could lead to spins.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would also move the mass outwards, i think this would make\u00A0the craft roll less well\u00A0(though not by too much).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOoh Ok, Your plane is much more sophisticated than the mine! ^^\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027ve put a pair of wing on a reverse-mounted engine, for me the most important part of the conception of a vehicle is the luck ! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TangerineSedge","CreatedById":150386,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T19:55:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/zepVN/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs promised, here are some pics of the rejected design. If you guys want, I can upload it to KerbalX for you to shoot at and maybe even improve slightly. However, you would need pWings(B9)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n--Edit--\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and yes, those are 40mm cannons under the wings\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-25T19:56:21Z\u0022 title=\u002202/25/2016 07:56  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 25, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by TangerineSedge\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T22:46:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429350\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456424488\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Doke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Doke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really like this design. Reminds me of something from Crimson Skies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, I followed the 3F rule on this one ... Form Follows Function\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ferram4","CreatedById":21328,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T00:26:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, a heads up to you guys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAssuming \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/72433-bahamutod/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002272433\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/72433-bahamutod/\u0022\u003E@BahamutoD\u003C/a\u003E ends up accepting the PR (when it\u0027s ready) and there are no serious bugs, and yada yada qualifiers, I\u0027ve got some AI modifications in store for BD pilots.\u00A0 Mostly I\u0027m tired of it turning into flat turning battle with whichever plane turns better / doesn\u0027t start the evasion code winning all the time and no AI coming to the other\u0027s aid.\u00A0 Right now I have it set up so that the AI will attempt to do Immelmanns, split-Ses, and chandelles as needed to conserve energy or get into position to attack the opponent.\u00A0 In addition, the AI will also call for help from its teammates when under fire, so it won\u0027t turn into a pair of independent dogfights 10 km apart.\u00A0 Right now I\u0027m working on making the evasion routine a bit smarter so that it actually tries to dodge the enemy plane\u0027s guns rather than just do something stupid and get killed or set up a really nice deflection shot for their opponent.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShould certainly make the battles more interesting, but at the same time will likely result in the design-meta favoring slightly different craft than before, so you guys should know.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Doke","CreatedById":149975,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T00:43:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/21328-ferram4/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002221328\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/21328-ferram4/\u0022\u003E@ferram4\u003C/a\u003E Sounds great! It seems like people are going for a wide mix of designs, anyway. I see turnfighters, low-drag energy fighters, weird speed demons, and all kinds of stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150386-tangerinesedge/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022150386\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150386-tangerinesedge/\u0022\u003E@TangerineSedge\u003C/a\u003E That thing is a beast. How fast is it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T01:39:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMOAR sliders to play with is always a good thing, love it\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TangerineSedge","CreatedById":150386,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T12:06:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222429966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456447414\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Doke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Doke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat thing is a beast. How fast is it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShe can easily reach 230m/s / 515mph / 830kph in level flight under 1k altitude. I never tested high altitude performance though, she was shelved when the AI couldn\u0027t handle her too well\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KamikazeF0X","CreatedById":104217,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T18:16:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222420818\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455990370\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250204\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tetryds\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 20/2/2016 at 6:46 PM, tetryds said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-align:center;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(227,47,41);\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003ERULES:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003ECraft:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n- Maximum of\u00A06 weapons of a single type on your airplane.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just realise, this means that we can have only one type of weapon\u003Cbr\u003E\nor\u003Cbr\u003E\nWe can have different weapons ( Like 2x12.7mm and a 1x23mm ) but we need to stay in the points limit, of course !\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd can we use a ball turret ? and does a ball turret counts for 25.4 points (Two times a 12.7mm MG)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T18:23:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222431001\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456510617\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KamikazeF0X\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, KamikazeF0X said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just realise, this means that we can have only one type of weapon\u003Cbr\u003E\nor\u003Cbr\u003E\nWe can have different weapons ( Like 2x12.7mm and a 1x23mm ) but we need to stay in the points limit, of course !\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd can we use a ball turret ? and does a ball turret counts for 25.4 points (Two times a 12.7mm MG)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo turrets allowed ... If you look back in the thread a few pages it was mentioned and explained why\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically any craft with a turret onboard ends up being invincible due to the way the AI handles target acquisition ... It is explained better a few pages back\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-26T18:28:53Z\u0022 title=\u002202/26/2016 06:28  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DoctorDavinci\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KamikazeF0X","CreatedById":104217,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T18:26:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222431010\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456511033\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo turrets allowed ... If you look back in the thread a few pages it was asked mentioned and explained why\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically any craft with a turret onboard ends up being invincible due to the way the AI handles target acquisition ... It is explained better a few pages back\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOoh didn\u0027t see that post, and it\u0027s a good news ! ^^\u003Cbr\u003E\nI have tested turrets and it\u0027s a 360\u00B0 of cheating freedom !!!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nEDIT :\u003Cbr\u003E\nIt\u0027s in the first page ... I go look for an optician!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-26T18:29:33Z\u0022 title=\u002202/26/2016 06:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by KamikazeF0X\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T18:32:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222431019\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456511178\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KamikazeF0X\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, KamikazeF0X said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOoh didn\u0027t see that post, and it\u0027s a good news ! ^^\u003Cbr\u003E\nI have tested turrets and it\u0027s a 360\u00B0 of cheating freedom !!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my experience the only thing that can target a turret equipped craft is another turret equipped craft however one of the teams has to be stationary\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-26T18:33:44Z\u0022 title=\u002202/26/2016 06:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DoctorDavinci\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tetryds","CreatedById":50204,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T20:38:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222431001\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456510617\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KamikazeF0X\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, KamikazeF0X said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just realise, this means that we can have only one type of weapon\u003Cbr\u003E\nor\u003Cbr\u003E\nWe can have different weapons ( Like 2x12.7mm and a 1x23mm ) but we need to stay in the points limit, of course !\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd can we use a ball turret ? and does a ball turret counts for 25.4 points (Two times a 12.7mm MG)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can have as many weapons as you want, as long as you dont have more than six of the same,\u00A0firing at the same time. And\u00A0stay on budget, of course.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo you can have 6 bredas long barrel and a few more short barrel, since they don\u0027t fire together.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is also a reason why different versions of the same weapon exist.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAbout turrets:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo turrets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are OP against the AI and there is no way to truly balance them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA turret would probably cost way more than that. Some changes to the AI may make it possible so a huge MAYBE for the next BAD-T\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wjolcz","CreatedById":39636,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T21:09:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill working on my entry. Making a flying wing combat-worthy is no easy task.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50204-tetryds/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002250204\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50204-tetryds/\u0022\u003E@tetryds\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0how many fighters/participants are you planning to accept? Is there a set limit?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T21:12:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShe\u0027s ready ... The DF-43 Bad Company is now in service\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWeight: Dry- 6.12t\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Loaded- 6.64t\u003Cbr\u003E\nArmament: 3x 23mm (1200 rounds)\u003Cbr\u003E\nTop Sustainable Speed: 247.4 m/s (890.6 Kph)\u003Cbr\u003E\nEffective Combat Speed: 70-200 m/s (252-792 Kph)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/76W6R/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-26T21:16:56Z\u0022 title=\u002202/26/2016 09:16  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DoctorDavinci\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MightyDarkStar","CreatedById":115126,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T21:16:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, \u003Cem\u003EWarspite \u003C/em\u003Etested in the new BDArmoury 10.3.3 AI. Took less than 2 minutes 20 seconds to completely execute the dummy. I need to update the craft file with the new AI settings however.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TangerineSedge","CreatedById":150386,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T21:17:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222431266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456521146\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShe\u0027s ready ... The DF-43 Bad Company is now in service\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWeight: Dry- 6.12t\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Loaded- 6.64t\u003Cbr\u003E\nArmament: 3x 23mm\u003Cbr\u003E\nTop Sustainable Speed: 247.4 m/s (890.6 Kph)\u003Cbr\u003E\nEffective Combat Speed: 70-200 m/s (252-792 Kph)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/76W6R/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell...this is embarrassing. My fighter seems to be *slightly* heavier than your heavy fighter...hmmm...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTime to send Jeb on a diet again ;P\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KamikazeF0X","CreatedById":104217,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T21:20:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222431266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456521146\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShe\u0027s ready ... The DF-43 Bad Company is now in service\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m happy to see that we are not in the same category ! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-26T21:25:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222431278\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456521477\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150386\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TangerineSedge\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, TangerineSedge said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell...this is embarrassing. My fighter seems to be *slightly* heavier than your heavy fighter...hmmm...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTime to send Jeb on a diet again ;P\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could shave a few more Kilo\u0027s off of her but she performs nicely the way she is although I may still tweak her control surfaces ... Still got a week or more till the competition starts but the DF-43 is done, I can\u0027t squeeze much more performance outta her than I\u0027ve already managed to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}